label: Times of Suriname
title: Times_of_Suriname
exrest: Times of Suriname is a national newspaper in Suriname. The paper is published daily in a broadsheet format with a reported circulation of 35,000-40,000. The paper was founded in December 2003 by rich business man and politician Rudi Dilip Sardjoe and claims to be a quality news paper and the largest and most-read paper of the country.
